title: Thank you for buying us a house!

media:group.media:title: Thank you for buying us a house!
media:group.media:description:
Teach yourself subjects in STEM with Brilliant, the natural partner to this channel! https://www.brilliant.org/simonclark

We're going to buy a house, and we're going to make the subscribers pay for it! With the support of my viewers over the past ten years, pixel girl and I have finally been able to buy a house. I wanted to make this house move in vlog to say thank you, both for enabling this particular life milestone, but also for sticking with me and for making the comments and discord and my social media replies such a wonderful community. I am so, so lucky to do this job, and to have a kind, generous, thoughtful group of people who enjoy the stuff I do. So thank you, so, so much.

My second channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/SimonClarkErrata

House move in day vlog, getting the keys to our first house, first time buyers, we bought our first house! In this move in vlog I say thank you for the support my YouTube subscribers have given to me and allowed me and my fiancee pixel girl to buy our first home together
